!README.md

# Local dev secrets & config -- must never enter a build context/image.
# Production values are supplied at runtime via env_file (.env.production),
# not baked in. Real values (JWT secrets, ENCRYPTION_KEY) live in these on a
# dev machine and packages/database/.env pins DATABASE_PROVIDER=sqlite for
# local dev, which would otherwise silently override the postgres build arg.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.production.example
